import erm1 from "../../assets/images/emergence-homepage.png";

const projects = [
  {

    name: "EMERGENCE",

    github: "https://github.com/AWSiegfried/Emergence_v1",
    imageOne: erm1,
    imageTwo: "../../assets/images/emergence-artistpage.png",
    imageThree: "../../assets/images/emergence-audio-features.png",
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    name: "NoGym",
    live: "https://nogym.herokuapp.com/",

    imageOne: "../../assets/images/nogym1.png",
    imageTwo: "../../assets/images/nogym2.png",
    imageThree: "../../assets/images/nogym3.png",
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    name: "Workout Tracker",
    live: "https://hwseventeen-workout-tracker.herokuapp.com/",
    github: "https://github.com/AWSiegfried/Emergence_v1",
    imageOne: "../assets/images/wt1.png",
    imageTwo: "../../assets/images/wt2.png",
    imageThree: "../../assets/images/wt3.png",
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    name: "Employee Directory",
    live: "https://awsiegfried.github.io/HW19-employee-directory/",
    github: "https://github.com/AWSiegfried/HW19-employee-directory",
    imageOne: "../assets/images/ed1.png",
    imageTwo: "../../assets/images/ed2.png",
    imageThree: "../../assets/images/ed3.png",
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    name: "Employee System",
    live: "https://github.com/AWSiegfried/HW12-employee-system",
    github: "https://github.com/AWSiegfried/HW12-employee-system",
    imageOne: "../assets/images/demo.gif",
    imageTwo: "",
    imageThree: "",
  },
  {
    id: 6,
    name: "Note Taker",
    live: "https://github.com/AWSiegfried/HW11-express-note-taker",
    github: "https://github.com/AWSiegfried/HW11-express-note-taker",
    imageOne: "../assets/images/emergence-homepage.png",
    imageTwo: "../../assets/images/emergence-artistpage.png",
    imageThree: "",
  },
];

export default projects;
